author: LegoDavid
title: A rare polybag that nobody cares about
review: I got this at a  LEGO store promotion for free. Very few people claim to own this set, and there is no ebay listing. So, I guess it's rare? Other than  the exclusive gray colored shield piece, this polybag is kinda useless. You get some nice parts, but other than that there is nothing special about it.
